The paper discusses the application of differential privacy for non-interactive publication of anonymized real-life datasets, which involves topics related to databases (cs.DB), cryptography and security (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
